00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:12.399
adhere to the national guidelines. And these MHSs, these municipal health services, have an

00:08:12.399 --> 00:08:21.519
advisory function on that as well. These 25 regions are subdivided into seven regions. And

00:08:21.519 --> 00:08:25.799
let's be honest, they've been in crisis mode for close to two years. And I think that that is a

00:08:25.799 --> 00:08:33.159
very important observation also concerning this talk. So this is the Netherlands. You all know

00:08:33.159 --> 00:08:39.520
this. This is the 25 municipal health regions. And this is where the Netherlands is situated. I

