And a lot of them actually

01:16:02.120 --> 01:16:04.120
started doing better in that regard.

01:16:06.120 --> 01:16:08.120
Yeah, great. It's that feedback loop

01:16:08.120 --> 01:16:10.120
that I think is really important

01:16:10.120 --> 01:16:12.120
that always

01:16:12.120 --> 01:16:13.120
needs to be called out.

01:16:13.120 --> 01:16:14.120
Great. Thanks.

01:16:14.120 --> 01:16:15.120
Definitely.

01:16:15.120 --> 01:16:16.120
Yeah, definitely.

