of something that could help the business

01:21:03.120 --> 01:21:05.120
or organization. What

01:21:05.120 --> 01:21:07.120
is one piece of feedback you

01:21:07.120 --> 01:21:09.120
would give them for

01:21:09.120 --> 01:21:11.120
just getting started with that first project?

01:21:11.120 --> 01:21:13.120
Start small.

01:21:13.120 --> 01:21:15.120
Just take something

01:21:15.120 --> 01:21:17.120
relatively simple.

01:21:17.120 --> 01:21:19.120
Make it

01:21:19.120 --> 01:21:21.120
look good.

01:21:21.120 --> 01:21:23.120
Once again, I'm sorry to emphasize

01:21:23.120 --> 01:21:25.120
this, but it is important. If you want to

01:21:25.120 --> 01:21:27.120
convince decision makers,

01:21:27.120 --> 01:21:29.120
then definitely do so.

01:21:29.120 --> 01:21:31.120
But start out with something

01:21:31.120 --> 01:21:33.120
small. And this is one of the reasons why

